AddressInfo.Title: Kristinehamn konstmuseum / Kristinehamn art museum
AddressInfo.AccessComments: On the building corner left of the main entrance around the corner there is a wall box with type 2 Mennekes connector. The place is marked with a car licence plate. It belongs to the museum. I approached the cashier and asked about charging, the answer was that charging will be okay as long as their own electric car is not on the spot. Please go in and ask the cashier in the museum shop before you connect!

GeneralComments: Type 2 wall box for the museum's vehicle. Ask receptionist/cashier first before connecting!
